import React from 'react'
import { Row, Col, Image } from 'react-bootstrap'
import adahi from '../images/adahi.jpeg'
import carla from '../images/carla.jpeg'
import carlos from '../images/carlos.jpeg'

export const Devs = () => {
  return (
    <Row>
      <Col>
        <Image src={adahi} className='imagen-devs' roundedCircle/>
      </Col>
      <Col>
        <Image src={carla} className='imagen-devs' roundedCircle/>
      </Col>
      <Col>
        <Image src={carlos} className='image-devs' roundedCircle/>
      </Col>
    </Row>
  )
}
